Create cart when user attempts to add item.


CONTROLLERS
==================

- Menu Item
	- Create

- Cart
	- Delete (Are you sure you want to clear you cart?)

User me = db.Users.Find(1);
me.Cart.GetCartTotal();
me.Cart.GetCartTax();
me.Cart.GetCartSubtotal();

- CartItem
	- Index (List items in user's cart / edit items)
	- Create[Post] (Redirect back to last menu location)
	- Edit[Post] (Redirect back to index)
	- Delete[Post] (Redirect back to index)

- Order
	- Index
	- Create (Add delivery address & credit card)
	- Details (Final Overview [Complete!])
	- Edit (Update delivery address & credit card)
	- Delete (Cancel Order)